  "title": "数星星",
  "titleEn": "Counting Stars",
  "emoji": "⭐",
  "paragraphs": [
    {
      "text": "晚上，天上有很多星星。一颗星，两颗星，三颗星……数也数不完。",
      "translation": "At night, there are many stars in the sky. One star, two stars, three stars... too many to count."
    },
    {
      "text": "月亮弯弯的，像一条小船。星星一闪一闪的，好像在对我眨眼睛。",
      "translation": "The moon is curved like a little boat. Stars twinkle, as if winking at me."
    }
  ],
